OL,3,CHave-a-go hero dragged along road by
OL,4,Crobbers' getaway car
OL,6,FA pair of robbers have been jailed
OL,7,Fafter a man was dragged for half a
OL,8,Fmile as he tried to stop their getaway
OL,9,Fcar.
OL,11,FThe man intervened when he witnessed
OL,12,FKeith Wilcox stealing a woman's
OL,13,Fhandbag in the car park of Morrisons
OL,14,Fsupermarket on Enterprise Way,
OL,15,FCastleford.
OL,17,FWilcox, 41, and his accomplice, 44-
OL,18,Fyear-old Lisa Burgess, sped off with
OL,19,Fthe man clinging to the Vauxhall Corsa
OL,20,Fthey were in.
