OL,3,CHave-a-go hero dragged along road by
OL,4,Crobbers' getaway car
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed him losing his
OL,7,Fgrip a short time later on Lumley
OL,8,FStreet, before the pair drove away.
OL,10,FThe victim suffered injuries to his
OL,11,Fhead and body, including a number of
OL,12,Ffractured ribs.
OL,14,FBurgess then attempted to use a bank
OL,15,Fcard which was stolen in the robbery.
OL,17,FShe pleaded guilty to robbery, fraud
OL,18,Fand causing injury by dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving and was jailed for three years.
