OL,4,Crobbers' getaway car
OL,6,FWilcox admitted robbery and was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 20 months.
OL,9,FPC Natalie Carr, of Wakefield district
OL,10,Fcrime team, said: "The male victim has
OL,11,Fshown immense bravery standing up
OL,12,Fagainst something that he knew to be
OL,13,Fwrong.
OL,15,F"We all have a part to play in
OL,16,Fchallenging violence against women and
OL,17,Fgirls and I know how thankful the
OL,18,Ffemale robbery victim is for his
OL,19,Factions.
