OL,6,F"Burgess put this man in extreme
OL,7,Fdanger by continuing to drive at speed
OL,8,Fknowing that he was holding on to the
OL,9,Fvehicle. Even with the knowledge that
OL,10,Fshe had left a man injured in the
OL,11,Froad, this did not deter her from
OL,12,Fattempting to use a bank card that was
OL,13,Fstolen in the robbery a short time
OL,14,Flater."
